{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"784c10b154","title":"《关于学习解放军加强政治工作的指示》的批示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"c80b4d1a84","index":0,"year":1964,"month":null,"day":null,"articleId":"784c10b154"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"994fc035d4","name":"工业战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"id":"e759231f2d","name":"农业战线","type":"主题/事件"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","name":"毛泽东思想万岁（1961年-1968年）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives3/main/45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce.pdf"},{"id":"maoquanji47","name":"毛泽东全集第47卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/47-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"4c3d391ff9","type":"paragraph","text":"六、男女关系上","index":0,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"784c10b154"},{"id":"236a7a8cda","type":"paragraph","text":"对男女关系问题，说起来津津有味，不是严肃的研究讨论，而是求得知识上的愉快。要谈恋爱不是政治第一，而是感情第一，甚至抱有自由主义态度。","index":1,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"784c10b154"},{"id":"1fb81a7690","type":"paragraph","text":"七、团洁观点上","index":2,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"784c10b154"},{"id":"f9bf113d62","type":"paragraph","text":"重视个人利益，固执己见，个人利签高于群众利签，领导能力强就服从，否期就看不起，发牢，分裂，你有一套，我也有一套，所谓文人相轻，行动自由，不管团结，许不允许，就开路一马司。","index":3,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"784c10b154"},{"id":"25f1f7ae1c","type":"paragraph","text":"八、在政治斗争上","index":4,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"784c10b154"},{"id":"98f6540bff","type":"paragraph","text":"夸大个人英雄主义作风，忽视了客观事物的发展规律，斗争性不强，不坚持原即和立场，易犯调和主义，不是过“左”就是过右。","index":5,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"784c10b154"},{"id":"8040713260","type":"paragraph","text":"九、群众观念上","index":6,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"784c10b154"},{"id":"3ec942350b","type":"paragraph","text":"喜欢爬在群众头上发号施合，不深入群众，对阶级没有明确的爱和，只是站在当中，对劳动大众可检，对地主无所谓。","index":7,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"784c10b154"},{"id":"639defad43","type":"paragraph","text":"《关于学习解放重加强政治工作","index":8,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"784c10b154"},{"id":"39ab0525c4","type":"paragraph","text":"的指示》的批示","index":9,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"784c10b154"},{"id":"053ee35faf","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六四年）","index":10,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"784c10b154"},{"id":"fc3aa04e78","type":"paragraph","text":"现在全国学习解放军、学大庆，学校也要学习解放军。解放军好，是政治思想好，也要向全国城市、农业、工业、商业、教育的先进单位学习。","index":11,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"784c10b154"},{"id":"75d1d551f2","type":"paragraph","text":"国家工业各部门，现在有人从上至下，即从部到广矿都学习解放军。设政治部，政治处和政治指导员，实行四个第一和三八作风-—看来不这样做是不行为，是不能提思整个工业部门（还有商业部门，还有农业部门）成百万成千万的干部和工人的革命精种的。","index":12,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"784c10b154"},{"id":"7522e2e8cf","type":"paragraph","text":"·208。","index":13,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"784c10b154"}],"page":{"id":"5abe1e7584","publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"784c10b154","start":221,"end":221}},"maoquanji47":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"1c832d2249","type":"title","text":"《关于学习解放军加强政治工作的指示》的批示","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"784c10b154"},{"id":"2e17dd6f8a","type":"paragraph","text":"国家工业各部门，现在有人从上至下，即从部到厂矿都学习解放军。设政治部、政治处和政治指导员，实行四个第一和三八作风——看来不这样做是不行的，是不能提起整个工业部门（还有商业部门，还有农业部门）成百万成千万的干部和工人的革命精神的","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"784c10b154"},{"id":"e18a9bd00d","type":"paragraph","text":"现在全国学习解放军、学大庆，学校也要学习解放军。解放军好，是政治思想好，也要向全国城市、农业、工业、商业、教育的先进单位学习。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"784c10b154"}],"page":{"id":"f604088974","publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"784c10b154","start":402,"end":402}}}},"__N_SSG":true}